import { Component, ElementRef, HostListener } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { LayoutService } from 'src/app/layout/service/app.layout.service'; import { TeamMember } from 'src/app/demo/api/teamMember'; import { Project } from 'src/app/demo/api/project'; @Component({ selector: 'app-landing', templateUrl: './landing.component.html', styleUrls:['./landing.component.scss'], }) export class LandingComponent { isNavbarGray = false; isResponsiveMenuGray: boolean = false; animationState = { highlights: 'hide', features: 'hide', pricing:'hide', certif:'hide', // Add more section IDs as needed }; images: string[] = [ 'assets/demo/images/landing/score.webp', 'assets/demo/images/landing/sflow1.webp', 'assets/demo/images/landing/sflow2.webp' ]; Project :Project[] = // Example projects data [ { image: 'assets/demo/images/landing/score.webp', title: 'Project 1', description: ' Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Molestiae earum similique delectus officia obcaecati aliquam autem provident cumque laudant', }, { image: 'assets/demo/images/landing/sflow1.webp', title: 'Project 2', description: 'Le dispositif médical WinnerFlow V3.0 est un embout buccal dexsufflation et insufflation qui permet la rééducation des muscles respiratoires du patient en inspiration et expiration. Le WinnerFlow V3.0 est destiné à un patient unique à usage multiple.', }, { image: 'assets/demo/images/landing/sflow2.webp', title: 'Project 3', description: ' Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Molestiae earum similique delectus officia obcaecati aliquam autem provident cumque laudant', }, // Add more projects as needed ]; teamMembers: TeamMember[] = [ { name: 'John Doe', position: 'Developer', image: 'https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/jese-leos.png' }, { name: 'Jane Smith', position: 'Designer', image: 'https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/jese-leos.png' }, { name: 'Jane Smith', position: 'Designer', image: 'https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/jese-leos.png' }, { name: 'Jane Smith', position: 'Designer', image: 'https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/jese-leos.png' }, { name: 'Jane Smith', position: 'Designer', image: 'https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/jese-leos.png' }, ]; constructor(public layoutService: LayoutService, public router: Router,public el: ElementRef) { } toggleNavbarColor() { this.isNavbarGray = true; } @HostListener('window:scroll', ['$event']) onScroll() { this.isNavbarGray = window.scrollY > 100; // Adjust the scroll position threshold const sections = ['highlights', 'features','pricing','certif']; // Add more section IDs as needed sections.forEach(section => { const offset = 100; const threshold = 0.3; const scrollPosition = window.scrollY; const windowHeight = window.innerHeight; const element = document.getElementById(section); if (element) { const elementPosition = element.offsetTop; const elementHeight = element.offsetHeight; const isVisible = scrollPosition + windowHeight > elementPosition + offset && scrollPosition < elementPosition + elementHeight - offset; this.animationState[section] = isVisible ? 'show' : 'hide'; } }); } ngOnInit() { // Initial check in case the component is already in view on page load this.onScroll(); } }

Notre vision

La vision de Med'In outlook consiste a étre un leader international dans le domaine de conception et developpement des dispositifs médicaux

Objectifs stratégiques

Notre mission est de répondre efficacement aux besoins et aux attentes actuels et futurs des partenaires de notre bureau d'études, de recherche et développement, dans le domaine de conception et le développement de dispositifs médicaux.

Notre mission

  • Assurer la disponiblité des ressources nécessaires afin de satisfaire les exigences de nos clients et les exigences réglementaires applicables
  • Renforcer d'une façon continue la compétence de notre personnel
  • Assurer l'amelioration continue au sein de notre organisme
  • Assurer une bonne communication en interne comme en externe
